description.en:
Core-Chip is a peer-to-peer cryptocurrency. It is neither a coin nor a token and therefore should be defined as a chip instead.

Core-Chip celebrates integration, thus in itself represents the integration of cryptocurrencies within assets.

Outabox Studios created Core-Chip as a rewards and payment system with the main purpose of integrating Core-Chip with all their upcoming games and projects.

Core-Chip is also the very first cryptocurrency to introduce the vein breaking system which releases Core-Chip on a yearly basis every time a vein breaks, the vein breaking system will remain active until the very last vein breaks.
